Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:23.45,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}This is different than making a sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.16,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}Something about it is different
