Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.00,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}So I just don't get why
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.46,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}I can't quite wrap my head around it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:41.47,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)\fscx90}but your existence is now much more than just important to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:47.43,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}There's nothing in this world that doesn't come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.77,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}I don't cry because I'm hurting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.44,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}They're the sweet, sweet drops of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.99,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}I want to go on dreaming forever, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.41,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(250,250)}I want to try and be more gentle, you know?
