Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Your dad always comes to pick you up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi's not my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a mum and a dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's Daikichi, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan says really weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Men can't have babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes one to know one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,Morons! Morons! Morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:43.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun called me a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.02,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun was calling us morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your family just you and your mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad ran off, so she divorced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "divorce" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when two grown-ups stop being married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's why my mum's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get scolded if you don't wear your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stretched the cord...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Someone's here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.53,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's here to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan... Someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Maa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we have for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's here to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mum's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a grumpy old lady at home, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always such a big help to Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My son's kind of blunt, so he doesn't make friends very easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's pretty quiet, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's a case of birds of a feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, you were talking about me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you telling me to carry you halfway again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a bit of a Daddy's girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of a relative, or... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, what am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice that you made a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun said he doesn't have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his dad got divorced and went off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what a divorce is, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When a marriage ends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If God knew about that, he'd probably punish those people, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my mum isn't here because of a divorce, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if she's like Kouki-kun's mum, I definitely do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too! {Oh Daikichi... XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan's mother is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think her mother is probably the maid who worked at Granddad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything about the maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A farewell party? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're having it so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders for winter clothing have finally died down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't really go out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid's only six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that you haven't been out drinking since...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It can't really be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've sort of stopped caring about drinking and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just too old for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only thirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, even though the guys in my department are young,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of them have kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's not really customary for them to go out drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go pick up my kid from nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife gave birth to two kids last year, and the younger one's only three months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I don't go straight home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She gives you hell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't want to make her mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about the farewell party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But night's not a good time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame to let it go to waste, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you bring her with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just looking for an excuse to go dr{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't worry! It'll be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming, coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi. Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Daikichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that your grandfather had a\Nregular maid dispatched by an agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find out her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshii Masako-san. The "masa" is the kanji for "correct", and the "ko" is the one for "child".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name on the mother and child health record, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to get in touch with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With the sort of person who left behind such a lovely{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Calm down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the health record, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole bunch of stuff written in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's still so much we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I can't tell the difference between work and home anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.42,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away! Damn drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is orange juice okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan's a beauty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gather it up for you, Yuu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san, you need to have a few more drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin might get sleepy on the way home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right... I'm going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He bailed on our department, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't produce results if you're only going to stop halfway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty ugly to just quit while you're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sales have taken a pretty bad turn this month, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if we do a decent job, the big shots are just going to compare it to last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The old me would've stormed in there with guns blazing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. I feel like I'm going to pee myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Little girls are really soft! {Oh dear... XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you were my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Some really important part of me has changed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About your transfer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand after meeting Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,I just want to squish you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotou-san, Rin-chan doesn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you feel about your kid? About Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu-kun was really cute, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure love little kids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! The mail's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It says here that they're having an informational meeting about junior school admittance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe this turned up without me doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an entrance test, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get in without taking any test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Compulsory education is great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Everyone else has left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun! Your mother's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kouki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been... a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, are we going to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grab a taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's name tags are reversible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that they can be hidden on the way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We also ask that you do not leave them alone, even at parks and places like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you make sure they don't go off with someone, even if it's someone familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to teach them to be suspicious of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...instead of trusting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that sheet we were given...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got them. I've got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know what vaccinations she's already had?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently that was a weird question to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Do you have Rin-chan's health record?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a page for recording it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I only met Rin about three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like she really trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks back a lot at home, and she nags me a bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just proof of her trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone could see that the two of you are a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A family...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just jumping over your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I said let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A school bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the fancy and designer ones'll be sold out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal one's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not. She's a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll have a look this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai-chan... Are you just going to keep raising Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You moved to another division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought that far ahead yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do yours this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are really close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mothers and daughters are like friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, Mum and Kazumi get along pretty well, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not impossible that Masako-san's situation could've changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that she'd want to live with her daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had so many shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess her mum really must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Boing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:56.70,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Daikichi is struggling to read because they've been written by someone who is computer illiterate, and half of the kanji have been entered incorrectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"If Masako found my will, she'd probably just destroy it,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"so I decided to go about things in a slightly more... bothersome way."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"But I can't work out how to properly hide this... or post this or anything like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"And this... keyboard thing is making fun of me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"so it's taking me forever to enter anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are some major kanji mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"My old body has grown terribly weary..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"...so I've decided to abandon this blog."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to have a little persistence when you're that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll continue the rest in Rin's health record."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rin. I'll just take a little look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"I trust that the person who finds this sheet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"...will be one who holds Rin close to his or her heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"I intend to record in here details pertaining to Rin and her mother, Masako."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Masako is the kind of person who is often misunderstood,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"so I wish to preface this by saying that she is by no accounts a terrible young lady."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"She feels that she isn't fit to be a mother,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"that it wouldn't be fair to Rin."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"She also insists on serving as my maid, even now,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"and I'm sure she will continue to do so."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I believe she feels as if that is the most she can do to make Rin happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To make Rin happy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"She lives every moment of her life while making sure that if anything were to happen to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"there would be no trace of her existence that any of my relatives would find."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is no doubt that Masako loves Rin as only a mother could."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yet she is still so young, and perhaps lacks the maturity to be a parent."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's clear that he really cared about Rin and her mother, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to make my hair look like bunny ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Reina-chan's mum did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I said do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said I wasn't cute.{;___;}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mii-chan said I wasn't cute at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Rin pretty much wins by default...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already grown up enough that comments like that really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realise, Masako-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that Rin's already so mentally mature?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no... There are parts of her that are, and parts that still aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why she needs an adult to look out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fin... ished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:40.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, star up in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.97,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glittering aw{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to keep the talent show a secret from our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Talent show?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's going to do it while wearing that hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:01.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, star up in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:05.41,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glittering away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you left Rin alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your twinkling eyes blink...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,telling yourself that it didn't matter if it was painful, because she'd forget in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:14.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as you watch over everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hate you without so much as a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.72,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, star up in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm praying that you at least had a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:23.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glittering away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of reason could actually make you leave your own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're going to be using it for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be better to go with something a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't a desk for a big girl be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A big girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! One for a big girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sitting there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like a big girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you could probably use that desk even once you're a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A high school student... Will I be a grown-up then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Maybe a half-grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me read!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"A girl went to play on her own in the forest."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"The girl got lost and looked for the path going back home."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"But she just couldn't find it."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Before she knew it, she came across a little house in the forest."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Yoshii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not again! Rin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to disappear on me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that'll make me into a big girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for much later on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sudden, so I'll show you some faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bored face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Embarrased face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi is going out to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But will he end up going out alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so important to him
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that he would even let me stay home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "Daikichi is my Daikichi."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"More" face.
